Quality Control on PDAC Mets Spatial Transcriptomics data from 10X

Ateeq Khaliq

2024-02-09

1 Introduction

The present script takes the summary of the spaceRanger output from the Spatial Transcriptomics data generated with 10X VISIUM technology on a set of PDAC Mets samples.

2 Getting Ready

We first load the libraries and set the paths to the raw data.

library(ggplot2)
library(vctrs)
library(patchwork)
library(Seurat)
library(tidyverse)
library(kableExtra)
library(RColorBrewer)
library(DT)

2.1 Metrics summary for all the samples.

QC_global_df <- read.table("/Users/merajam/Downloads/pdac_combine_metrics.txt",sep="\t" , row.names = 1, header= TRUE)
datatable(QC_global_df, options = list(scrollY = "300px",paging = FALSE))
cat("\n\n\n\n\n\n\n")

2.2 Number of Spots Under Tissue - Pre QC

colors <- c('#1f77b4','#ff7f0e','#2ca02c','#d62728','#9467bd','#8c564b','#e377c2','#7f7f7f','#bcbd22','#17becf','#FFBB78','#1b9e77','#FF5733','#6A5ACD','#FF1493','#32CD32','#00FFFF','#FFD700')
par(mar = c(10, 4, 4, 2) + 0.1)
barplot(QC_global_df$Number_of_spots_PreQC, col = colors, names.arg=rownames(QC_global_df), las=2)

cat("\n\n\n\n\n\n\n")
